data.enText: to make sth bigger; to become bigger

data.chText: 已经有了扩大娱乐场地的计划。
data.enText: There are plans to enlarge the recreation area.
to make a bigger copy of a photograph or document

data.chText: 我们准备将这张照片放大。
data.enText: We're going to have this picture enlarged.
to say or write more about sth that has been mentioned

simple_means.memory_skill: en 使… + large 大 → 扩大

ex.chText: 他通过这种乐器把声音扩大了。
ex.enText: He amplified the sound through the musical instrument.

synonyms.bx: 指放大声音等，尤指音乐声。

ex.chText: 扩大农场/扩建酒店/放大相片
扩大词汇量的一个有效办法就是看报纸。
ex.enText: An effective way to enlarge your vocabulary is to read newspapers.

synonyms.bx: 指放大尺寸、面积、容量等。

ex.chText: 20世纪70年代，该城市的人口迅速增加。
ex.enText: The city's population expanded rapidly in the 1970s.

ex.chText: 古城墙被拆掉，城区被扩大了。
ex.enText: The ancient city walls were demolished and the urban area was expanded.
The number of female students has increased.
They had to increase their investment.

ex.chText: 我们必须增加工业生产。

data.enText: to say or write more about sth that has been mentioned

tr: add details, as to an account or idea
clarify the meaning of and discourse in a learned way, usually in writing
example: She elaborated on the main ideas in her dissertation

value.def: When you enlarge something or when it enlarges, it becomes bigger.

example.ex: ...the plan to enlarge Ewood Park into a 30,000 all-seater stadium...
example.tran: 将伊伍德公园球场扩建成能容纳3万座席的体育场的计划

example.ex: The glands in the neck may enlarge.
The UN secretary-general yesterday recommended an enlarged peacekeeping force.
example.tran: 联合国秘书长昨天建议扩充维和部队。

value.def: To enlarge a photograph means to develop a bigger print of it.

example.ex: ...newlyweds wishing to enlarge snaps of their big day.
example.tran: 希望把他们大喜之日的照片放大的新婚夫妻

value.def: If you enlarge on something that has been mentioned, you give more details about it.

example.ex: He didn't enlarge on the form that the interim government and assembly would take...
example.tran: 他没有进一步说明过渡政府和立法机构将采取的形式。

example.ex: I wish to enlarge upon a statement made by Gary Docking.
example.tran: 我想就加里·多金的话再展开说一下。

value.tran: 进一步补充;详述;详细说明
